latestIgtvVideos.title: A3Charge
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Long day draining all the battery from your devices? Need a quick battery recharge but forgot your power bank at home?
A3Charge @a3charge_ has come to the rescue! 
A rental power bank service with dispensing machines across Delhi NCR. 
Its easy, quick and a saviour. One just needs to download the app, check the nearest A3Charge station, scan the QR code and Voila!

The power bank can be returned to any nearby A3Charge station. 
A3Charge powerbank comes with multiple types of cables, compatible with most devices. 

Dont worry about your devices running out of battery and enjoy charging on the go with A3Charge! @24sevenin @24seven.in @looksunisexsalon
